Example Single-Cell RNA-Seq Counts

Source: R/datasets.R
singleCellCounts.Rd

Modified version of scater::sc_example_counts, with dimnames formatted in camel case for package consistency.

singleCellCounts

Format

An object of class dgCMatrix with 2000 rows and 40 columns.
